service

public void service(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                    javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response)
             throws IOException,
                    javax.servlet.ServletException
Handles a servlet request by dispatching it to a handler. It receives a servlet request, translates it into an exchange object, dispatches the exchange to a handler, then translates the exchange response into an servlet response.
